    Operator <-->|HTTPS| Dashboard
    Dashboard <-->|HTTP/JSON| API
    API <-->|SQL| Postgres
    API <-->|RESP / Streams| Redis
    API -->|telemetry spans/metrics| OTLP
    API -->|LLM requests| OpenRouter
    Redis -. events .- Dashboard
    Postgres -. audit logs .- OTLP

